Name: Panco's Journey
About the game: Panco's Journey is a 2D Platformer puzzle game where you incarnate Panco , a white little cat, on his journey in Elemalia . Panco has the ability to shapeshift with the help of Elemalia's residents. You can transform up to 3 different elements , each accompanied by their unique movements and interactions . Water form : Where you can swim in water and climb waterfalls! Fire form : Where you float, can get carried by wind and burn wood! Electric form : Where you can travel in iron wires and dash on a short distance! You can interact with many objects of the world to draw yourself a way through the level! Grab coins on the level to unlock new zones and continue your journey!
